These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, dancer
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, november
House: craftsman, futuristic
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the craftsman house##1
2. the dancer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Job   | dancer    | analyst |
| Birthday         | november | february    |
| House     | craftsman     | futuristic      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, fantasy
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, librarian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the engineer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Movie-Genre      | fantasy  | time-travel   |
| Job   | librarian | engineer  |
| Birthday     | june   | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
City: miami, san-francisco
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, june
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| City         | miami   | san-francisco  |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea  |
| Birthday         | august   | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, ebony
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, brazilian
1. the chinese is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Color          | blue | ebony |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | lemonade   |
| Nationality     | brazilian       | chinese      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
2 different games are played: bridge, chess
House: cottage, wooden
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, december
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Game        | bridge      | chess  |
| House       | wooden     | cottage    |
| Birthday   | june | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, social-worker
2 different pets are kept: turtle, fish
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, american
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the bartender##1
2. the australian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Job         | bartender    | social-worker    |
| Pet   | fish     | turtle      |
| Nationality         | australian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
House: art-deco, palace
2 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard
2 different games are played: chess, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
3. the art-deco house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| House    | palace | art-deco     |
| Pet     | lizard | mouse |
| Game   | poker | chess    |

 #################################

 
