.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-10::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, amber
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, house
1. the fan of house is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who likes lavender is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |
| Color   | amber | lavender     |
| Transport       | scooter        | snowmobile    |
| Music-Genre      | r&b  | house |

