.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, begonia
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, july
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Pet           | turtle     | goldfish |
| Flower   | begonia | iris  |
| Birthday     | july      | february |

