.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, mango
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Food         | mango | pineapple |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | mystery     |
| Transport           | snowmobile          | bus     |

