.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, writer
City: rome, miami
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, aristoff
1. the librarian is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Job   | librarian | writer |
| City   | rome  | miami  |
| Cigar     | aristoff | siglo    |

 